=== Pronunciation ===
[[Category:Hebrew language]]
ירא / yârê' / yaw-ray'
=== Etymology ===

A primitive root; 
=== Verb ===
to [[fear]]; morally to revere; causatively to frighten: - affright, be (make) afraid, dread (-ful), (put in) fear (-ful, -fully, -ing). (be had in) reverence (-end), X see, terrible (act, -ness, thing).